      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... there isn't anything \"important\" to reevaluate. that's the whole problem. we just make up these little stories to keep ourselves busy so we don't have to face the fact that we're just biological accidents. it's all just a loop of suffering for no reason. why even keep trying to find meaning when it's fundamentally not there?",
